<div class="app-status-box">
    <h3 class="govuk-heading-m">Formatting</h3>
    <p class="govuk-body"><strong>How to create a link</strong></p>
    <p class="govuk-body">Use square brackets [] around the text you want to be a link. Use round brackets () around the URL for the link. Make sure there are no spaces between the brackets.</p>
    <p class="govuk-body">For example: [GOV.UK](https://gov.uk) will show as <a class="govuk-link" href="https://gov.uk">GOV.UK</a></p>
    <p class="govuk-body"><strong>How to create bullet points</strong></p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>Use asterisks (*) to create a bullet point
    </li>
    <li>Make sure there is one space after the asterisk
    </li>
    <li>leave one empty line space before the bullet points start, and one after
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p class="govuk-body">For example:</p>
  <ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>list item 1
    </li>
    <li>list item 2
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
